dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Portage County, WI 2020
dc_description_s: This data represents hydrography for Portage County, Wisconsin in 2020 and includes the layers 'Portage_Hydro(poly)_2020' and 'Portage_Hydro(line)_2020'. [This data contains polygons representing lakes, ponds, rivers and streams that are at least 15 feet wide. Attributes include Name, Navigibility (if known), alternate name, and a link to WiDNR bathymetric maps.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://www.co.portage.wi.gov/375/Land-Information-GIS
